title: Communications to the National Academy of Sciences
additional-note: This is a monographic series that includes papers reprinted from other publications.  Before concluding an issue is in the public domain, search for renewals for it under its distinctive title.  If the issue's contents originally appeared in another publication, check to see if that publication has copyright renewals. We have not systematically checked individual issues of this serial, but have only verified that no renewals have been filed under this serial's title.
acknowledgement: Thanks to Pete Sullivan for copyright research on this title.
